title: A Record Breaking Esports Prize Pool - Kinda Funny Games Daily 08.15.2019
description:
Quip starts at just $25 and if you go to http://getquip.com/GAMES right now, you can get your first refill pack for FREE.

Boost is only available at http://Experian.com/kfgames

Time stamps - 
00:03:43 - Housekeeping
The KF crew is going to the Canadian National Exhibition in Toronto this weekend! August 16-18, Greg, Tim, and Andy will be hosting two panels a day in the Gaming Garage! Head to kindafunny.com/events for all the details.
What’s Good Games is throwing a party at PAX West and you’re invited! We’re once again partnering with Square Enix and Life is Strange for Relax at PAX 2019 - this year we’ll be at Art Marble 21 from 7-10pm on Friday Aug. 30th.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Black Jack and Mohammed Mohammed
